= Publications

See also my [https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=U1TGq_gAAAAJ Google Scholar]
and [https://arxiv.org/a/bao_j_2 arXiv] pages. Author names are listed alphabetically
following the theoretical computer science convention.

. *On estimating the quantum Tsallis relative entropy*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.00752 arXiv]\] \n
  with Minbo Gao and Qisheng Wang

. *Quantum algorithms and lower bounds for eccentricity, radius, and diameter in undirected graphs*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2502.20148 arXiv]\] \n
  with Adam Wesołowski

. *Learning junta distributions, quantum junta states, and $\mathrm{QAC}^0$ circuits*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.15822 arXiv]\] \[AQIS 2025\] \[ICML 2026\] \n
  with Francisco Escudero Gutiérrez

. *On quantum time complexity of divide and conquer*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2311.16401 arXiv]\]
  \[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Vc9FzULV_E QIP 2024]\] \[ICALP 2025\] \n
  with Jonathan Allcock, Aleksandrs Belovs, Troy Lee, and Miklos Santha

. *Constant-depth circuits for uniformly controlled gates and Boolean functions with application to quantum memory circuits*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2308.08539 arXiv]\]
  \[[https://quantum-journal.org/papers/q-2024-11-20-1530/pdf Quantum]\]
  \[QTML 2023\]
  \[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=66hoGm5TRWc TQC 2024]\] \n
  with Jonathan Allcock, João Doriguello, Alessandro Luongo, and Miklos Santha

. *Fundamental theorem for quantum asset pricing*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.13815 arXiv]\] \n
  with Patrick Rebentrost

. *Quantum algorithm for stochastic optimal stopping problems with applications in finance*
  \[[https://arxiv.org/abs/2111.15332 arXiv]\]
  \[[https://drops.dagstuhl.de/storage/00lipics/lipics-vol232-tqc2022/LIPIcs.TQC.2022.2/LIPIcs.TQC.2022.2.pdf TQC 2022]\] \n
  with João Doriguello, Alessandro Luongo, Patrick Rebentrost, and Miklos Santha
